== 評價 ==
本作在[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上，根據48條評論，獲得38％的認可率，平均評分為4.9/10。該網站的用戶們認為「此作擁有完善的科幻設定，而有足夠動作戲吸引觀眾觀看，儘管觀眾們不會留下深刻印象<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/outside_the_wire|title=Outside the Wire (2021)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|access-date=2021-01-15|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019211342/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/outside_the_wire|dead-url=no}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。」而[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則根據10位評論家得出的平均分為47/100，獲得了「好壞參半」的評級<ref>{{cite web |title= Outside the Wire Reviews |url= https://www.metacritic.com/movie/outside-the-wire |website= [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher= [[Red_Ventures|Red Ventures]] |access-date= 2021-01-15 |archive-date= 2021-01-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210116110020/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/outside-the-wire |dead-url= no }}{{cbignore}}</ref>。

[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的大衛·埃里克給電影定了C級，並寫道：「（編劇）的努力令此作成為Netflix上少數成功的科幻電影，其中亦討論了一些大問題，例如另一部科幻片《[[超能查派|超能查派]]》，談論了現代戰爭的影響<ref>{{cite news |last1= Ehrlich |first1= David |title= ‘Outside the Wire’ Review: Anthony Mackie Is an Android Soldier in Netflix’s Silly Future ‘Training Day’ |url= https://www.indiewire.com/2021/01/outside-the-wire-review-netflix-1234609669/ |accessdate= 2021-01-15 |work= [[IndieWire|IndieWire]] |date= 2021-01-15 |archive-date= 2021-01-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210116160025/https://www.indiewire.com/2021/01/outside-the-wire-review-netflix-1234609669/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。」

